{"tid":584884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原諒基亞連尼咁直：熱刺條命就係失敗！","createTime":"2018-03-08T07:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T08:11:43.000Z","uid":4661,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1be7ca11d01054536e185b59de894f4d1d713a","tid":584884,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180308/photo/bkn-20180308142648617-0308_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180308142658\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180308%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180308142648617-0308_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180308142658&h=2017a718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱刺近年異軍突起，一眾年輕新星亦大獲好評，不過每次去到關鍵時刻都會自動甩轆，今晨歐聯16強輸畀祖雲達斯出局後，祖記中堅基亞連尼賽後寸爆，話熱刺「條命就係失敗」：「熱刺有好多好波之人，但我哋知道佢哋經常自爆，呢樣嘢已經寫咗喺熱刺歷史入面，佢哋製造好多機會，但永遠都係差啲啲，歷史唔到你唔信。」"},{"pid":"4548c5779495e575a1ef4de9e61499581f6219d1","tid":584884,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:42:50.000Z","msg":"係咪可以行得番出球場興奮到傻左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次對我熱準備定棺材啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n享受下我熱既無犯規落地獄腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc04cdd632daeff24c2cb5e5dbbea9ae2cca39c","tid":584884,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;... It&rsquo;s the history of Tottenham, they always create many chances and score so much but at the end they miss something to arrive in the end. We believe in the history. I think also yesterday in the game between Real and Paris, the history is important.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b585989251f14377e4793c8ad4e2662a69af6df","tid":584884,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"中文幾好"},{"pid":"db74e85efb07e21f43ac0df619acefe85b4eb9fc","tid":584884,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b585989251f14377e4793c8ad4e2662a69af6df","tid":584884,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"中文幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  譯都懶, 直接鳩up 出黎"},{"pid":"afd1f850f38b1e57b3165b887f3b015806d0fa8a","tid":584884,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fc04cdd632daeff24c2cb5e5dbbea9ae2cca39c","tid":584884,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;... It&rsquo;s the history of Tottenham, they always create many chances and score so much but at the end they miss something to arrive in the end. We believe in the history. I think also yesterday in the game between Real and Paris, the history is important.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"gabriel clarke<br />\n@gabrielclarke05<br />\n<br />\nChiellini&rsquo;s brutal verdict:&rsquo;we knew Spurs were weak in defence and fragile mentally- experience told&rsquo; @itvfootball"}]}